msgid ""
"The Dev MCP tools section is appended during the Quarkus build by the `aggregate-skills` Maven goal.\n"
"Only tools that are enabled by default are included.\n"
"All modules are scanned via Jandex on compiled classes.\n"
"The enriched skills are baked into the `quarkus-extension-skills` JAR published with each Quarkus release."
msgstr "在 Quarkus 构建过程中 `，aggregate-skills` Maven 目标会将“Dev MCP 工具”部分追加进去。仅包含默认启用的工具。所有模块都会通过 Jandex 对编译后的类进行扫描。增强后的技能会被整合到随每个 Quarkus 版本发布的 `quarkus-extension-skills` JAR 文件中。"

